0.9.name: wordpress/wp-amasin-the-amazon-affiliate-shop
0.9.description:
WP AMAZON enables you to open your own Amazon Affiliate Shop at your Blog. You can easily search for products to add to your shop. The Plugin works with all Amazon Affiliate Programs including: * http://www.amazon.com * http://www.amazon.ca * http://www.amazon.de * http://www.amazon.co.uk * http://www.amazon.co.jp * http://www.amazon.cn * http://www.amazon.es * http://www.amazon.it * http://www.amazon.fr
